{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1696-05_121", "resp": "wordpro"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Réponse de Mademoiselle d’Alerac, à Mademoiselle l'Heritier"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", mai 1696 [tome 5], p. 121-124."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "RÉPONSE"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[1]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[2]", "text": "De Mademoiselle d’Alerac,"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[2]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "À Mademoiselle l’Heritier."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Que je sçay bon gré, Mademoiselle, au spirituel inconnu qui vous donne le nom de Telesille ! Il vous convient, si quelque chose peut vous assortir. Je vous l’aurois donné, ce nom, si je n’estois persuadée que le vostre vaut mieux que tous ceux dont l’on peut se servir. Si vous aviez vêcu dans ces siecles reculez, vous auriez rempli l’Histoire. Alors l’on auroit décidé pour les Anciens ; mais il vaut mieux que nos Neveux lisent ce qui vous distingue par mille beaux endroits, & que nous jouïssions de l’heureux plaisir de vous voir, qui doit estre si cher à vos Amis."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "L’on trouve en vous une amitié solide,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": " Un commerce plein de douceur."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Quand sur vos beaux endroits il faut que l’on décide,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": " Quelque bon goust qui guide,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "L’un tient pour vostre esprit, l’autre pour vostre cœur."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Il n’y a que l’amour qui se plaint de vous. Il est vray, Mademoiselle, que vous le bravez sans ménagement."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": " Pour avoir plus d’esprit qu’une autre,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": " Croyez-vous sauver vostre cœur"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "  D’une tendre langueur ?"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "  C’est une pure erreur."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": " Ce cœur est fait comme le nostre,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Dans vos Vers immortels vous chanterez un jour"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": " La gloire de l’amour."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Il sera seur de triompher lors que vous ferez valoir ses charmes."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": " Vos Vers ont un tour enchanteur,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "L’amour verra par eux augmenter son empire."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": " Telesille, il n’est point de cœur"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Qui ne se rende au son de vostre docte Lyre."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[4]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[4]/text()[1]", "text": "L’amour me sçaura bon gré de mon préjugé, & peut-estre par reconnoissance, laissera-t-il mon cœur à l’amitié, qui est si contente de moy, & qui a tant de raison de l’estre. Vous me faites sentir, Mademoiselle, tout ce qu’elle a d’agreable par le plaisir que j’ay d’aimer, & d’estre aimée d’une Amie de vostre merite. Je suis."}]}]}]}